These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, ritmeester, aristoff, bongani
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, pink, yellow, amber
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, rabbit, pony
House: gothic-revival, colonial, craftsman, victorian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, tram, scooter
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip, sunflower, lily
 1. the victorian house is on the far right##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 5. the bongani-smoker is the person who likes amber##1
 6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the craftsman house is between the person who growsdahlia and the person driving the scooter##2
 8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is between the craftsman house and the person who likes amber##2
11. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
12. the victorian house is the owner of the pony##1
13. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the bike and the owner of the rabbit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Cigar      | bongani        | ritmeester       | aristoff  | baccarat |
| Color          | amber     | yellow         | pink     | ivory    |
| Pet         | goat  | cat      | rabbit   | pony     |
| House           | colonial | gothic-revival | craftsman   | victorian     |
| Transport   | bike    | tram         | airplane | scooter         |
| Flower         | lily     | dahlia     | tulip  | sunflower       |

